







       Menus should be used to organize a collection of basic con-
       trols in a horizontal, vertical, or 2-dimensional layout
       within a separate Menu window.  There are three types of
       Menus: PullDown, Popup, and Option.  A Menu is only avail-
       able while it is posted.



















       Menus follows the navigation model described in Chapter 2.
